article.headline: Alabama A&M beats Oakwood 81-61.
article.story:
HUNTSVILLE, Ala. --  Alabama A&M picked up its first victory of the season by defeating Oakwood 81-61 on Saturday night.

The Bulldogs took off to a 45-24 lead at halftime en route to the victory.

Alabama A&M (1-2) opened the season with road losses at Dayton and Georgia Tech.

The Ambassadors are members of the United States Collegiate Athletic Association.
